<h1><%= current_page.data.title %></h1>

<p class="mt-4">At DSKI we offer so much more than a school. We offer an enjoyable and stimulating journey from one year old up to eleven years old. We strive to develop our students into well-rounded, multilingual global citizens who will have a passion for learning for life and a desire to make a change in the world. </p>
<p>Under the expert guidance and care of our teachers, your child will flourish in an environment incorporating a wide range of subjects through our programmes, and co-curricular activities.</p>
<p>We offer a wide range of pursuits, activities and services to make sure your child's development and your family's experience is world-class.</p>
<span id="languages"></span>

