        <%= image_tag 'photos/about_3_800px.jpg', alt: data.config.title, class: 'rounded img-fluid' %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 pl-5">
        <p class="lead text-uppercase">Physical Education</p>
        <h2>Swimming lessons at DSKI</h2>
        <p>At DSKI, all students take swimming lessons until age 10. Swimming is a skill for life and we place a strong emphasis on safety and fun in the water. The swimming lessons are incorporated into the timetable and students get used to this as part of their weekly schedule. We have fully-trained instructors teaching swimming at the Kobe Municipal pool which is a short bus ride away. Students are required to bring swimwear and a towel on their swim days.</p>
        <p><%= link_to 'Find out more here', local_path('about/physical-education') %></p>
        <span id="clubs"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

