      <p class="lead text-uppercase">Clubs</p>
      <h2>After School Extracurricular Clubs at DSKI</h2>
      <p>At DSKI we offer a range of after school extracurricular​ ​activities​. From performing arts, sports, crafts, calligraphy, coding, cooking and Makers Club we hope we can offer something stimulating, fun and healthy for your child. There is a minimum number of students required in order for the club to run so please let us know the club you would like to join and hopefully we can run it.</p>
